entry.summary: Take advantage of the unique tax benefits associated with superannuation. Since superannuation contributions are not taxed as your income, you can acquire more Bitcoin compared to traditional investment channels. Long-term holders benefit immensely, as self-custody means the Bitcoin always remains in your control, allowing you to grow your retirement savings on your terms.

entry.summary: Manage your retirement savings by making you the sole custodian of your Bitcoin. With full access to your wallet, only you or your designated will can authorize the movement of coins. Our platform enables you to create complex signing schemas for your self-custody, ensuring your investments are secure and accessible, even in unforeseen circumstances like your death.
